description:
My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 5 Episode 24

Manu Feildel and Pete Evans return to host and judge the ultimate home-cooking battle!

It's time to hit the road in Melbourne as our teams are pushed to their limit by Irish chef Colin Fassnidge as they separate into two groups and each run a restaurant from the MKR Food Truck. The group that earns the most money will be safe from elimination. The weakest group will head to Kitchen Headquarters to battle against each other for their right to stay in the competition. Hosted by Manu Feildel and Pete Evans.
